Description: Terminal music CLI with web UI and extensive features
 mox is a powerful command-line music player that provides:
 .
  * Multiple audio sources (YouTube, SoundCloud, Bandcamp, local files)
  * Beautiful web interface with real-time synchronization
  * Rich terminal interface with progress bars and visualizations
  * Real-time synced lyrics from lrclib.net
  * Terminal album art display via chafa
  * Playlist management and sharing capabilities
  * Auto-DJ mode with Last.fm recommendations
  * Bookmark system for saving queue states
  * Comprehensive listening history with search and export
  * Fast search using YouTube Data API v3 integration
  * Advanced audio controls (volume, speed, equalizer, crossfade)
  * Extensive queue management and manipulation tools
 .
 The application uses mpv as its backend for reliable audio playback
 and supports cross-platform operation on Linux and macOS systems.